@startuml
!theme plain
title 21. Heterogeneous GP-GPU Governance
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName DejaVu Sans
left to right direction

rectangle "Workload request" as N1 #D6EAF8
rectangle "Capability profiles" as N2 #D5F5E3
rectangle "NVIDIA/AMD/Intel pools" as N3 #FCF3CF
rectangle "Collectives/RDMA" as N4 #E8DAEF
rectangle "Scheduler placement" as N5 #FADBD8

N1 --> N2 : SLO + model
N2 --> N3 : vendor/runtime traits
N3 --> N4 : eligible devices
N4 --> N5 : communication path

note bottom
Actor-facing contract: lower-layer resource identifiers remain hidden unless the ADR explicitly defines them as operator-only evidence.
end note
@enduml
